== His son was also notable ==
Sir Samuel Gerald Wood Burston (born 24 April 1915) was a grazier and agricultural administrator; President of the National Farmers' Federation; Member of the Reserve Bank Board 1977-87; OBE 1966 for fire-fighting; Knight Bachelor 1977 for services to primary industry.  

